<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<meta name="description" content="I build simple automation tools that remove repetitive business work like spreadsheets, emails, and data tasks.">
<title>Automation Demo | Collins Isibor</title>

<style>
    * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, sans-serif;
        background: #f7f7f7;
        color: #1a1a1a;
        line-height: 1.6;
        padding: 2rem 1rem;
    }

    .container {
        max-width: 760px;
        margin: auto;
    }

    .card {
        background: #fff;
        border: 1px solid #e6e6e6;
        border-radius: 12px;
        padding: 1.6rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    }

    h1 {
        font-size: 30px;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    h2 {
        font-size: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
    }

    p {
        font-size: 15px;
        color: #333;
    }

    .sub {
        color: #555;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .btn {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 0.8rem;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        background: #fff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        cursor: pointer;
        font-size: 14px;
    }

    .btn:hover {
        background: #f2f2f2;
    }

    .list {
        list-style: none;
        margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    .list li {
        padding-left: 1.2rem;
        margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
        position: relative;
    }

    .list li::before {
        content: "→";
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        color: #666;
    }

    input, textarea {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 0.7rem;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-size: 14px;
        margin-top: 0.3rem;
    }

    label {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #444;
    }

    .note {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #777;
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 0.8rem;
    }

    .footer {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #888;
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <div class="card">
        <h1>I automate repetitive business tasks</h1>
        <p class="sub">
            If you spend too much time on spreadsheets, emails, or copying data between tools — I can help you turn that into a simple automation.
        </p>

        <button class="btn" onclick="document.getElementById('form').scrollIntoView({behavior:'smooth'})">
            Tell me what you’re struggling with
        </button>
    </div>

    <!-- WHO I AM -->
    <div class="card">
        <h2>Who I am</h2>
        <p>
            I’m Collins, a technical virtual assistant and automation developer. I build small tools that remove repetitive work in businesses using Python and simple workflows.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top:0.5rem;">
            I focus on practical solutions — not complex systems.
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- WHAT I CAN AUTOMATE -->
    <div class="card">
        <h2>What I can help you automate</h2>
        <ul class="list">
            <li>Spreadsheet cleaning and organization</li>
            <li>Email sorting and simple workflows</li>
            <li>Lead or customer data processing</li>
            <li>Repetitive admin tasks</li>
            <li>Simple business operations tasks</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
    <div class="card">
        <h2>How it works</h2>
        <ul class="list">
            <li>You tell me the task that wastes your time</li>
            <li>I study it and build a simple automation</li>
            <li>I record a short Loom showing how it works</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- SOCIAL PROOF (REALISTIC) -->
    <div class="card">
        <p style="font-style: italic;">
            “He helped me simplify a spreadsheet workflow I used to do manually every week. It saved a lot of time.”
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top:0.5rem; font-size:13px; color:#666;">
            — Small business client
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- FORM -->
    <div class="card" id="form">
        <h2>Tell me your task</h2>
        <p class="sub">
            I’ll record a short Loom showing how I’d automate it. No pressure, no charge.
        </p>

        <form action="https://formsubmit.co/collinzpy@gmail.com" method="POST">
            <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="New Automation Request">
            <input type="hidden" name="_captcha" value="false">

            <label>Name</label>
            <input type="text" name="name" required>

            <br><br>

            <label>Email</label>
            <input type="email" name="email" required>

            <br><br>

            <label>What task is wasting your time?</label>
            <textarea name="task" rows="4" required></textarea>

            <br><br>

            <button class="btn" type="submit">
                Send → Get my free demo
            </button>
        </form>

        <p class="note">
            I only reply with a short Loom video showing how I’d solve your problem.
        </p>
    </div>

    <!-- FOOTER -->
    <div class="footer">
        Collins Isibor • Automation Developer & Technical VA <br>
        <a href="mailto:collinzpy@gmail.com">Email</a> | 
        <a href="https://github.com/collinzpy">GitHub</a>
    </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
